column2: SELECT   b.ra AS lam_ra,b.dec AS lam_dec,   a.ra AS SDSS_ra,a.dec AS SDSS_dec, a.petroMag_u, a.petroMag_g , a.petroMag_r , a.petroMag_i , a.petroMag_z into mydb.cross_petroMag from mydb.cross_mag as b      CROSS APPLY fGetNearestObjEq(b.ra,b.dec,#) as c      JOIN DR1#.PhotoObjAll AS a ON a.objid = b.objid
